в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ store/
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ products.store.ts
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ models/
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ product.models.ts
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ products.routes.ts
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ users/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ store/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ models/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ users.routes.ts
в”‚
в””в”Ђв”Ђ settings/
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ store/
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ settings.routes.ts
```

**Rules for `/features`:**
- Folder names describe **business capabilities**
- Each feature is **self-contained**
- One **smart component** (container) per feature
- Multiple **dumb components** as needed
- Feature-specific store, models, and services live inside
- Routes are lazy-loaded
- Features should not directly import from other features

