## Smart vs Dumb Components

### Smart Components (Containers)
```
features/{feature}/components/{feature}-container/
```

Responsibilities:
- Inject store and services
- Manage lifecycle (connect/disconnect)
- Orchestrate child components
- Handle events from children
- NO direct DOM manipulation

### Dumb Components (Presentational)
```
features/{feature}/components/{component-name}/
shared/components/{component-name}/
```

Responsibilities:
- Receive data via `input()`
- Emit events via `output()`
- Render UI based on inputs
- NO injected services (except pure utilities)
- Highly testable and reusable

## File Naming Conventions

| Type | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Component | `{name}.component.ts` | `product-card.component.ts` |
| Service | `{name}.service.ts` | `product-api.service.ts` |
| Store | `{name}.store.ts` | `products.store.ts` |
| Model | `{name}.models.ts` | `product.models.ts` |
| Pipe | `{name}.pipe.ts` | `truncate.pipe.ts` |
| Directive | `{name}.directive.ts` | `tooltip.directive.ts` |
| Guard | `{name}.guard.ts` | `auth.guard.ts` |
| Interceptor | `{name}.interceptor.ts` | `error.interceptor.ts` |
| Routes | `{feature}.routes.ts` | `products.routes.ts` |

## Import Aliases

Configure in `tsconfig.json`:

```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": {
      "@core/*": ["src/app/core/*"],
      "@shared/*": ["src/app/shared/*"],
      "@features/*": ["src/app/features/*"],
      "@env/*": ["src/environments/*"]
    }
  }
}
```

Usage:
```typescript
// вњ… Correct: Use path aliases
import { ApiService } from '@core/services/api.service';
import { ButtonComponent } from '@shared/components/button/button.component';
import { ProductStore } from '@features/products/store/products.store';
import { environment } from '@env/environment';

// вќЊ Incorrect: Relative paths across boundaries
import { ApiService } from '../../../core/services/api.service';
```

## Barrel Files (index.ts)

Export public API from each module:

```typescript
// shared/components/index.ts
export * from './button/button.component';
export * from './card/card.component';
export * from './loading-spinner/loading-spinner.component';

// Usage
import { ButtonComponent, CardComponent } from '@shared/components';
```

## Routing Structure

```typescript
// app.routes.ts
export const routes: Routes = [
  { path: '', redirectTo: 'dashboard', pathMatch: 'full' },
  {
    path: 'dashboard',
    loadChildren: () => import('@features/dashboard/dashboard.routes')
      .then(m => m.DASHBOARD_ROUTES)
  },
  {
    path: 'products',
    loadChildren: () => import('@features/products/products.routes')
      .then(m => m.PRODUCT_ROUTES)
  },
  { path: '**', redirectTo: 'dashboard' }
];

// features/products/products.routes.ts
export const PRODUCT_ROUTES: Routes = [
  {
    path: '',
    component: ProductListContainerComponent
  },
  {
    path: ':id',
    loadComponent: () => import('./components/product-detail/product-detail.component')
      .then(m => m.ProductDetailComponent)
  }
];
```
